			<!-- <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">plans</h2> -->
			<ul>
				<li><b>by the public, for the public</b>: data dumps will be released weekly under a public domain license</li>
				<li><b>ethical data collection</b>: data contribution will be opt-in</li>
				<li><b>privacy friendly</b>: hashing access point identifiers protects personal information from being leaked</li>
				<li><b>abuse resistant</b>: published data cannot be used to create fake observations</p>
